# Claude settings (.claude/settings.json, .claude/settings.local.json) are
# intentionally tracked — single-author project, workflow/permission setup
# should migrate with the repo across machines.

# Overnight-batch result archives. The active CSVs in
# overnight_results/ change with each batch run, but archives of past
# runs (named archive_YYYY-MM-DD_pre-<commit>) are local-only — they
# can always be re-derived from the relevant commit by re-running the
# batch. Tracking them would bloat the repo without adding signal that
# isn't already in the perf_history.md narrative.
overnight_results/archive_*/
